"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.2.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.2.1</span> 標題：帳棚門、分隔的幔子（door of tent, dividing curtain）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： דֹּק</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： doq)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:22\">ISA 40:22</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： יְרִיעָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： yri‘ah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:2\">PSA 104:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:5\">SNG 1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:2\">ISA 54:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:20\">JER 4:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:20\">JER 10:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:29\">JER 49:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:7\">HAB 3:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： αὐλαία</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： aulaia)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt14:14\">JDT 14:14</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>幔子將大帳棚的內部隔成幾個空間。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>希伯來文<em>yri‘ah</em> 起初指覆蓋帳幕的罩棚（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.15.2.3.6.1 細麻布幔子 (linen cloth strips)&lt;REALIA:3.15.2.3.6.1&gt;</a> ）。在上面列出的大多數經文中，該詞與一個意為「帳棚」的詞平行對應。因此，它有時似乎是帳棚的換喻詞（比較<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:2\">2SA 7:2</a> 「上帝的約櫃在<em>yri‘ah</em> 裡面」和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:1\">1CH 17:1</a> 「耶和華的約櫃在<em>yri‘ah</em> 下面」）。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:2\">PSA 104:2</a> 中，「鋪張諸天，如鋪<em>yri‘ah</em> 」的視覺意象源於帳幕中的幔子在約櫃上方展開。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt14:14\">JDT 14:14</a> 說，「巴哥阿就進去，敲了帳棚的門」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 直譯）。這種表達在英文中很不自然，在其他一些語言中也同樣奇怪。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New American Bible (1970)\">NAB</abbr> 和<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Revised Standard Version (1989)\">NRSV</abbr> 試圖通過把「門」（希臘文<em>aulaia</em> ）改成「入口」來解決這個問題。還有譯本的改動更大，如「巴哥阿就進去，在帳棚的睡覺區域前拍手」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直譯）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> 的譯法更接近<em>aulaia</em> 的字面意思，英文意為：「巴哥阿進到帳棚裡面，拍打分隔帳棚的幔子。」敘事的重點是，巴哥阿以為敖羅斐乃和友弟德是在床上，姿勢不雅，便製造出響動，以防突然進去而驚嚇到他們。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
